headline: Millrose Properties Q4 Earnings Call Highlights
summary: Millrose Properties (NYSE:MRP) outlined accelerating adoption of its homesite “land banking” model in its fourth-quarter and full-year 2025 earnings call, describing 2025 as a proving year for the company’s permanent-capital approach and setting expectations for additional growth in 2026. Business
